### 🧪 ASP.NET Core Framework HTTP Test Client

# Konfigurasi Environment
@hostname = localhost
@port = 5000
@host = http://{{hostname}}:{{port}}

###
# 1. Test DI Lifetimes (Bandingkan GUID)
# Jalankan request ini 2x, perhatikan:
# - GUID transient1 vs transient2 berbeda.
# - GUID scoped1 vs scoped2 sama, tapi berganti saat request berikutnya.
# - GUID singleton1 vs singleton2 selalu sama di setiap request.
GET {{host}}/api/framework/lifetimes

###

# 2. Test Validation Filter (Valid Model)
POST {{host}}/api/framework/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Habibie",
  "value": 42
}

###

# 3. Test Validation Filter (Invalid Model)
POST {{host}}/api/framework/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Hb",
  "value": 150
}
